Navbar

Fixed position (scroll karne pe upar hi rahega)
Left: Logo (AVYRON)
Center: Home, Collection, Contact
Right: "Add to Cart" icon
Add to Cart click → ek modal khulega — cart mein jo products hain wo row-list (card jaisi horizontal rows) mein dikhenge, har row pe ek "Remove" button hoga
Collection → dropdown (hover/click pe) — jismein categories links ke roop mein dikhengi (Men/Women/Unisex, jo bhi DB se aaye)
Mobile → hamburger menu (☰) mein convert ho jayega

1️⃣ Hero Banner

AVYRON branding + tagline + CTA button
3 images ka auto-slider — har 3 second mein khud badlengi (carousel)

2️⃣ Categories

3 columns, ek row mein — Men, Women, Unisex saath saath
Mobile pe bhi 3 hi ek row mein rahenge (chhote size mein, wrap nahi honge)

3️⃣ 6 Products

Homepage pe 6 featured/latest products, neeche "View All" button (poori list page pe le jayega)

4️⃣ About Brand

4 images + text — text main khud likh dunga (brand tone ke hisaab se, aap review kar lena)

